description: 133 Echelon Seaport, Junior 1 Bed / Studio Residence w/1 garage parking. Unit 1621 is thoughtfully designed to enhance your lifestyle. Whether you're working from home or savoring a cup of coffee, you'll love the amazing natural light that floods this unit. Modern kitchen features white oak cabinetry & high-end appliances. Stylish sleeping area defined by custom molding. Plank flooring & thoughtful attention to detail throughout. Echelon Seaport residents enjoy over 50,000 square feet of resort-style amenities, including 1 indoor pool, 2 outdoor pools, hot tub, Sky Lounge w/ patios, & versatile meeting spaces. State-of-the-art fitness facilities feature an indoor basketball court, golf simulator, & yoga room. The 5th-floor Club Level boasts a lounge w/ fireplace, library, private dining/wine room, and outdoor terraces equipped with grill stations & fire pits. Residents benefit from 5-star services as well as easy access to incredible retail & dining options.
